# New Features of RTO app:
★ Latest News With Pagination ⇒ Read the latest news related to bikes, cars, trucks and other vehicles
★ Speed Meter ⇒ View your driving speed on a speedometer in analogue, digital and map mode
★ Mileage calculator ⇒ Calculate the mileage of cars and bikes
★ Loan calculator ⇒ Fill in the required details to calculate loan
★ Vehicle expense manager ⇒ Manage your vehicle maintenance expenses
